Lydia Ourahmane (amụrụ n'afọ 1992, Saïda, Algeria) bụ onye na-ese ihe na-arụ ọrụ na Algiers. E gosipụtara ọrụ ya na mba ụwa na ebe nke gụnyere Ca' Pesaro, Louisiana Museum of Modern Art, Manifesta, Kunstverien München. Ebe ngosi nka ọhụrụ, Chisenhale Gallery, Istanbul Modern the Centro per l'Arte Contemporanea Luigi Pecci, Zachęta National Gallery of Art, Institute of Contemporary Arts, World Museum na Wattis Institute for Contemporary Arts.
Ọ gụsịrị akwụkwọ na Mahadum Goldsmiths nke London n'afọ 2014.
